   Here's a table of English to Pirate translations

   ==========   ==============
   English      Pirate
   ==========   ==============
   sir              matey
   hotel        fleabag inn
   student      swabbie
   boy              matey
   madam        proud beauty
   professor        foul blaggart
   restaurant       galley
   your         yer
   excuse       arr
   students     swabbies
   are              be
   lawyer       foul blaggart
   the              th'
   restroom     head
   my               me
   hello        avast
   is               be
   man              matey
   ==========   ==============

   Write a program that asks the user for a sentence in English and then translates that
   sentence to Pirate.
   ~~~~